<item>
            <title>[LU-13935] ofd_attr_set and ofd_destroy do not properly handle object removal</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13935</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Improper object existence handling can lead to the following crashes:&lt;/p&gt;
